A permaculture to satisfy everyone within the home itself, even better! 

This is a place for models describing how to view the world of free and open production, ending miserable work by visually modeling existing processes of production, from materials production/extraction to product reuse or recycling. The goal of this page is to have in practice an enjoyable, publicly modifiable, 'product life-cycle management' web program that can alter or leave fallow our dear planet Earth by the most life nurturing means known possible. 

